6. Act phase
I actually couldn’t find a complete relationship between factors but surely, there is a connection between some of them that affect one another in some way. For example, Active hours is contributing to burning calories but it is not the only reason it could be training or a physical job, and the same thing to how many steps participants walk per day it is a huge factor but I can see that some of them has lower steps and burning lots of calories.
Another fact is I found out that there is no relationship between sleep and burning calories.
To summarize the analysis, I would advise the company to create an app to track their clients’ activities and a reminder to drink water and when should someone go to bed. Moreover, I would create an app to track their nutrition and give them a diet plan based on their type of life and body. I will also give the clients a 2-month free trial so we can own their trust and at the same time they will get used to our products and they will stick with them after
 














































